      "csl:pageColumn": "1,2",
      "rdf:value": "<L>107<pc>1,2<k1>aMh<k2>aMh<h>1<e>1\r\n<hom>1.</hom> <s>aMh</s> ¦ (<ab>cf.</ab> √ <s>aNG</s>) <ab>cl.</ab> 1. <ab>Ā.</ab> <s>aMhate</s>, to go, set out, commence, <ls>L.</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to approach, <ls>L.</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/> <ab>cl.</ab> 10. <ab>P.</ab> <s>aMhayati</s>, to send, <ls>Bhaṭṭ.</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to speak, <ls>Bhaṭṭ.</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to shine, <ls>L.</ls><info verb=\"genuineroot\" cp=\"1Ā,10P\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
